Maintainer: Andrea M. Kipingu <akipingu@ihi.or.tz>
Description: An R package providing simulation-based power analysis to inform the design of robust semi-field vector control experiments. It includes support for random effects and empirical p-value extraction, power estimation and parallelized workflows.
